pageProduct.name: Schick Hydro 5 Sense Sensitive Mens Refill Razor Blades 4pk
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Schick Hydro 5 Sense Sensitive Refill helps protect your skin from irritation with its 7 hydrating gel pools that hydrates throughout each shave.

Boxed Contents: 4 cartridges

Size: 4 Pack

Skin Type: Sensitive

KEY FEATURES

• Skin guards help reduce irritation.

Warnings

Blades are sharp tools, handle with care. Keep away from children.

Ingredients

Peg-115M, Titanium Dioxide, Zinc Stearate, Cyclodextrin, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Calendula Officinalis Flower, Camellia Sinensis Leaf, Hydrogenated Jojoba Oil, Panthenol, Sodium Hyaluronate, Tocopherol, Maltodextrin, Aqua.
